Hairline design and placement.
 A simple, straight forward, almost mechanical method of drawing the hairline is presented.
 It is amazing to see how this method, when followed closely, consistently produces a natural, aesthetically pleasing result on all sizes and shapes of heads.
 It is recognized by the authors that there are a lot of individual variations among hair transplant surgeons and most will be very attractive and quite natural.
 However, we believe that the following description will provide a good starting point in designing hairlines, and if the basic points are followed, unnatural hairlines will be avoided.
